(2340,43,13,'false_120363407223719821@g.us_3A8ACF5CC5DE01CBB185_211750578348127@lid','inbound','chat','Ultra-realistic live awards ceremony.\nGrammy / Academy Awards cinematic prestige atmosphere. Multi-camera broadcast style mixed with intimate handheld documentary shots. Natural human reactions, no overacting.\n\nAudio: elegant orchestral music, crowd murmur, microphone reverb, loud applause, cheering, footsteps, chair movement, realistic stage sounds.\n\nLighting: warm golden stage spotlights, cooler audience lighting, LED wall reflections, moving broadcast lights. Spotlight locks onto winner after announcement.\n\nSetting: massive luxury awards venue with giant LED screens, elegant podium, orchestra pit, thousands of formally dressed guests, press cameras, live overhead broadcast screens.\n\n@image_1 — STRICT WINNER IDENTITY “Aysholpan”\nPreserve exact face, body, skin tone, proportions.\nOutfit: elegant formal evening look (soft pastel / lavender tones inspired by original outfit), refined accessories, award-appropriate styling. No face modifications.\n\n@image_2 — STRICT HOST IDENTITY\nPreserve exact face and build.\nOutfit: black tuxedo, white shirt, black bow tie, polished formal shoes.\n\n15-SECOND TIMELINE:\n\n0–3s:\nBroadcast close-up on @image_2 at podium under golden spotlight. He slowly opens envelope, pauses dramatically, looks into camera and says in English Latin script:\n“The Best Actress is… Aysholpan!”\nCrowd murmurs quietly.\n\n3–6s:\nHard cut to audience. TV camera pushes through rows and finds @image_1 seated among guests. Spotlight instantly locks onto her. Genuine shock crosses her face, then emotional smile. Guests around her stand, clap, cheer, and lightly touch her shoulders in congratulations.\n\n6–9s:\n@image_1 stands and walks toward stage. Handheld documentary camera tracks beside her with subtle natural shake. Giant overhead screens show her live face feed. Loud applause fills venue. She walks calmly, emotional but composed.\n\n9–12s:\nCamera follows @image_1 up stage stairs into bright spotlights. @image_2 smiles warmly and presents award statuette with both hands. @image_1 receives it naturally. Brief handshake and genuine smile between them. Massive LED wall behind displays:\n“AYSHOLPAN”\n“BEST ACTRESS”\nwith glowing celebratory graphics and a giant portrait of @image_1.\n\n12–15s:\nWide cinematic broadcast shot of full stage. Standing ovation across venue. @image_1 stands center stage holding the award proudly while @image_2 applauds beside her. Giant LED wall blazing behind them. Dramatic golden lighting, roaring crowd, emotional awards-show finale. No fade to black.',NULL,NULL,'Алтынай Қайратқызы',NULL,0,NULL,'delivered','2026-05-08 20:00:04','2026-05-08 20:00:05','2026-05-08 20:00:05'),
